profile_positions.description:
Within the Benelux Sales team, the Account Development Officer is the one who, together with the Account Manager, maintains all customer contacts, takes up and follows up on both internal and external projects. This role is key in winning new business plus keeping and expanding existing customer relations.

- Set up quotes based on the required customer-, project, and price information. Finalize it together with the Key Account Manager and co-ordinate, maintain and implement price agreements;
- Co-ordinate and initiate project activities and monitor & guard progress of the project;
- Co-ordinate the whole sample process with regard to sending samples and gathering feedback. Including informing the Key Account Manager and other parties involved of this feedback;
- Act as the first contact for and pro-active inform customers with all projects, customer questions, plus organize and set up customer visits;
- Serve as question beacon for several internal departments with regard to agreements, questions and complaints. Independantly deal with it and involve the Key Account Manager where necessary;
- Administrate sales and customer information in the required systems.
